  "title": "Enabling routing makes Instantsearch fail in IE-11",
  "body": "**Bug: Enabling routing prevents instantsearch from loading in IE-11**\r\n\r\n**Expected the result to be similar to using urlSync: true**\r\n\r\n**Bug only affects IE-11**\r\n\r\ntest configuration:\r\n`var search = instantsearch({\r\n\tappId: algolia_config.appId,\r\n\tapiKey: algolia_config.apiKey,\r\n\tindexName: algolia_config.index,\r\n\trouting: true\r\n});`\r\n\r\nThe console in IE-11 shows:\r\n`SCRIPT438: The object does not support the property or method 'assign'\r\ninstantsearch.js (30004,7)`\r\n\r\n",
